CHEESES: LOW MOISTURE MOZZARELLA (PASTEURIZED MILK, CHEESE CULTURE, SALT, ENZYMES), PROVOLONE (PASTEURIZED MILK, CHEESE CULTURE, SLAT, ENZYMES), ASIAGO (PASTERURIZED MILK, CHEESE CULTURE, SALT, ENZYMES), PARMESAN (PASTEURIZED MILK, CHEESE CULTURE, SALT, ENZYMES), ROMANO MADE FROM COW'S MILK (PASTEURIZED COW'S MILK, CHEESE CULTURE, SALT, ENZYMES). COOKED ITALIAN SAUSAGE: PORK, SPICES AND FLAVORINGS, WATER, SALT, SUGAR, SODIUM PHOSPHATE, PAPRIKA, CARAMEL COLOR. MAY CONTAIN NATURAL SMOKE FLAVORING, SODIUM PHOSPHATE. GARNISH: DEHYDRATE GARLIC, OREGANO, PARSLEY.
